//000000000000a:40:{s:2:"id";s:5:"28585";s:4:"body";s:395:"<p>柏克和阿伦特等思想家把博爱和同情视为感伤主义，是滥情、不理智的表现，认为结果会<span style="text-decoration:underline;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>，达不到改善弱者境遇的效果。贫困等问题的解决还是要靠政治，而非部分人的善心。<br>填入划横线部分最恰当的一项是（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）。</p>";s:7:"bd_desc";s:0:"";s:7:"options";s:141:"[{"cs":"A ", "text":"适得其反"},{"cs":"B ", "text":"事与愿违"},{"cs":"C ", "text":"南辕北辙"},{"cs":"D ", "text":"雪上加霜"}]";s:11:"description";s:302:"<p class="item-p">文段后文语境强调“达不到改善弱者境遇的效果”，可见填入的成语辨析应与此一致。“事与愿违”指事情没能按照预想的方向发展，即文中的“达不到……的效果”，填入文段符合语境。因此，本题答案为B选项</p>";s:7:"dp_desc";s:0:"";s:6:"answer";s:1:"B";s:8:"wrongans";s:0:"";s:6:"status";s:1:"1";s:10:"optiontype";s:1:"1";s:8:"bigtype1";s:21:"言语理解与表达";s:10:"smalltype1";s:12:"逻辑填空";s:10:"pointtype1";s:12:"成语辨析";s:5:"tagid";s:1:"0";s:6:"chance";s:1:"0";s:6:"ismock";s:1:"1";s:5:"qyear";s:4:"2009";s:5:"views";s:1:"0";s:6:"rorate";s:1:"0";s:7:"usetime";s:1:"0";s:10:"materialid";s:1:"0";s:4:"diff";s:1:"0";s:7:"addtime";s:1:"0";s:10:"updatetime";s:1:"0";s:10:"supplierid";s:1:"2";s:8:"sourceid";s:5:"33605";s:8:"insertid";s:1:"0";s:6:"extend";s:4:"null";s:5:"skill";s:4:"null";s:7:"bigtype";s:1:"1";s:9:"smalltype";s:1:"7";s:9:"pointtype";s:2:"29";s:6:"tagids";N;s:7:"errnums";s:1:"1";s:8:"collects";s:1:"0";s:5:"marks";s:1:"0";s:5:"notes";s:1:"0";s:4:"bugs";s:1:"0";s:7:"loglist";N;s:9:"pointname";s:12:"成语辨析";}
